. \n\nIt's like draining your savings account to zero and calling yourself richer. \n\nIt's OK not to understand oil markets. \n\nIt's not OK to pretend you do, @DavidInglesTV \n\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket", "time": "02:16", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 19826, "likes": 258, "replies": 14, "retweets": 20, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": null}, {"id": "2073994748151611661", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2073994748151611661", "text": "ADNOC today launched a global LNG\nmarketing and trading platform in Abu Dhabi Global Market (ADGM), combining the marketing activities of ADNOC Gas and XRG with the trading capabilities of ADNOC Trading into an\nintegrated commercial platform. #OOTT #Adnoc", "time": "04:57", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 17303, "likes": 65, "replies": 6, "retweets": 22, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074004028699414748", "url": "https://x.com/LukeyTrags/status/2074004028699414748", "text": "The world is transitioning to hydrocarbons @realhagetaka #OOTT #COM $OIL $COAL", "time": "05:34", "author": "LukeyTrags", "author_name": "Hydrocarbon", "followers": 5697, "views": 2380, "likes": 19, "replies": 1, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074011792670404784", "url": "https://x.com/printtie_offcl/status/2074011792670404784", "text": "티티가 추천하는 오늘의 프린티! #OOTT📺\n\n'999' 작가님의 작품을 감상해보세요 !\n📞...뭐라고요? 괴담출근 3부 복귀가 드디어 내일이라고요?!😱\n#괴담에떨어져도출근을해야하는구나 #괴담출근_3부복귀 #최솔 \n\n@999storage\nhttps://t.co/qUbjWxxNjk", "time": "06:05", "author": "printtie_offcl", "author_name": "프린티 공식", "followers": 2022, "views": 4648, "likes": 45, "replies": 0, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074052815870448006", "url": "https://x.com/refineryritolia/status/2074052815870448006", "text": "🚢 Busy day in the SoH.\n\nThe Iranian routing lane is packed with crude tankers—possibly the largest simultaneous transit in more than 100 days. An encouraging sign is that vessel traffic through this critical chokepoint is improving, though it remains below pre-war levels. #oott https://t.co/ec6ZjVC9", "time": "08:48", "author": "refineryritolia", "author_name": "Sumit Ritolia", "followers": 402, "views": 3180, "likes": 14, "replies": 2, "retweets": 8, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074066953870909948", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2074066953870909948", "text": "PSA: China is starting to buy again.\n\n#oott", "time": "09:44", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 42465, "likes": 188, "replies": 6, "retweets": 32, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 34, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074087599636135936", "url": "https://x.com/Energy_Tidbits/status/2074087599636135936", "text": "Imagine if this was a stock market graph instead of a climate warming graph.\n\nInvestors would be piling more money into the market.\n\nGraph from \"Extreme Heat Isn't the Only Climate Impact Shocking Scientists\". Thx @business @eroston @hellococomo \n\n#oott \n\nhttps://t.co/nivub1Raq5 https://t.co/eTYAp6o", "time": "11:06", "author": "Energy_Tidbits", "author_name": "Dan Tsubouchi", "followers": 15856, "views": 2226, "likes": 15, "replies": 3, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074105592885461149", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074105592885461149", "text": "Saudi Aramco cuts the official selling price (OSP) for Arab light for Asia by USD 11.00/bbl to USD -1.50/bbl versus the benchmark (Oman/Dubai average) for the month of August  #oott", "time": "12:18", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6077, "likes": 34, "replies": 1, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074105860796694677", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074105860796694677", "text": "UAE crude output nears record following OPEC exit, sources says\nThe United Arab Emirates raised its crude ‌output to near record highs above 3.8 million barrels per day in June\n #oott https://t.co/oMjuiRzRfG", "time": "12:19", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5593, "likes": 29, "replies": 3, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074112960738287982", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2074112960738287982", "text": "Speculators are almost all on the same side of the boat. \n\nBrent net longs are near record lows while shorts hover near record highs. \n\nCrowded trades can persist—but they rarely end quietly.\n\n #Oil #OOTT #Brent #EnergyMarkets #Macro", "time": "12:47", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 7814, "likes": 72, "replies": 4, "retweets": 12, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074115919618478487", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2074115919618478487", "text": "Oil markets have swung from fearing a supply shock to pricing a glut\n\nBut production hasn't surged & demand hasn't collapsed. \n\nA traffic jam is clearing, the risk premium has evaporated & sentiment has flipped. \n\nThat's not the same thing as a new oil reality. \n\n#Oil #OOTT #Brent #Hormuz #EnergyMar", "time": "12:59", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 5494, "likes": 78, "replies": 1, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074133047234941231", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074133047234941231", "text": "Ukrainian drones hit Russia's largest refinery, in one of deepest strikes yet\n#oott https://t.co/KqI83Nc6zB", "time": "14:07", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6423, "likes": 10, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074137776690250106", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074137776690250106", "text": "Saudi Aramco official selling prices (OSP) for Arab light in USD/bbl vs the respective benchmarks #oott https://t.co/FjZ3ld6j3L", "time": "14:25", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5581, "likes": 27, "replies": 0, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074142589284958588", "url": "https://x.com/OilandEnergy/status/2074142589284958588", "text": "Up to 75% of pre-war oil flows through the Strait of Hormuz could return by year-end, but analysts warn lower prices aren't guaranteed. FGE says lasting peace between the U.S. and Iran is \"impossible to imagine,\" keeping geopolitical risk alive. #Oil #OOTT #Iran \n\nhttps://t.co/tuBlkjhdch", "time": "14:45", "author": "OilandEnergy", "author_name": "OilPrice.com", "followers": 96445, "views": 4201, "likes": 22, "replies": 3, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074170124718817317", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074170124718817317", "text": "US SPR crude inventories fell by ~6.2mb w/w to a multi year low of 319.5mb last week #oott        \n\nSour down ~2.7mb to 202.8mb    \nSweet down ~3.4mb to 116.7mb https://t.co/c8ihfX5SNU", "time": "16:34", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 71349, "likes": 185, "replies": 8, "retweets": 37, "quotes": 13, "bookmarks": 25, "labels": null}, {"id": "2074171496948199823", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074171496948199823", "text": "#Russia's anti-monopoly watchdog opens case against six independent filling station operators in Moscow Region owing to simultaneous price increases\n#oott https://t.co/pCRgSlkFJA", "time": "16:39", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 7403, "likes": 4, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "20